By implementing these recommendations,  the [portfolio](../../Advanced%20Investments/An%20Asset%20Allocation%20Primer.md) manager can optimize the [portfolio](../../Advanced%20Investments/An%20Asset%20Allocation%20Primer.md)'s risk-return profile while maintaining alignment with [investment](../../Advanced%20Investments/An%20Asset%20Allocation%20Primer.md) objectives.

